{"tid":1531791,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Apink初瓏普美周日香港見面會宣布延期","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:35:28.000Z","uid":74065,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e014cfb4a2a693a522e41bc8f5c076a018b778","tid":1531791,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190902/photo/bkn-20190902174723673-0902_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190902175735\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190902174723673-0902_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190902175735&h=21e50742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n初瓏（左）與普美原定本周日在香港舉行見面會，今日宣布延期。<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團Apink成員朴初瓏及尹普美原定周日（8日）在旺角舉行粉絲見面會「ChoRong &amp; BoMi Hong Kong Fan Meeting [夏日的初春]」，但主辦單位今日在Facebook宣布是次見面會將會延期：「鑑於最近香港社會環境不可預料的變動，及考慮到藝人、觀眾及工作人員的安全，遺憾地宣布原定2019年9月8日假旺角麥花臣場館舉行之『ChoRong &amp; BoMi Hong Kong Fan Meeting [夏日的初春]』將會暫時延期，亦希望盡快協調最終延期定案，再為大家帶來精彩的演出。"},{"pid":"4f0bef1c85e2f8c14e105344bbe8781a4056b681","tid":1531791,"uid":194940,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"佢地平安就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4733ea1753c7b13cf082db884c484991f3a466c2","tid":1531791,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e966d0fd19a344cb4cf5edac53496a3cb4ec2b8b","tid":1531791,"uid":190258,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"plan a最後嘅良心"},{"pid":"28cf0589d99dcfea4dbbb00a73681c92e2dd4f96","tid":1531791,"uid":61748,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p